The Fish that Climbed Trees: A Journey of Self-Discovery - This movie follows the journey of a fish named Finley who discovers a hidden talent for climbing trees. As Finley navigates the unfamiliar world above water, he learns to embrace his unique abilities and finds a new sense of purpose. Along the way, he meets a group of friends who encourage and support him, helping him to believe in himself and his dreams.

Finley's Fishy Adventures - In this animated series, Finley and his friends explore the ocean and its many wonders. As he delves deeper into the city, he uncovers a sinister plot to destroy the ocean and its inhabitants. With the help of his friends, Finley must use his climbing skills to navigate the treacherous underwater world and stop the villain before it's too late.
